  "short_description": "<table class=\"table\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"product-detail__specification-title\">Single basket washing</th>\n<td class=\"text-right\">No possibility</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"product-detail__specification-title\">Presence of cutlery basket</th>\n<td class=\"text-right\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h4>ENERGY / PERFORMANCE INFORMATION</h4>\n<table class=\"table\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"product-detail__specification-title\">Cleaning performance</th>\n<td class=\"text-right\">A</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"product-detail__specification-title\">Maximum temperature for water intake (Ã?Â?Ã?Â°C)</th>\n<td class=\"text-right\">60</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"product-detail__specification-title\">Noise level (dBA)</th>\n<td class=\"text-right\">46</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"product-detail__specification-title\">Energy efficiency class</th>\n<td class=\"text-right\">E</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"product-detail__specification-title\">Energy consumption annual (kWh/annum)</th>\n<td class=\"text-right\">266</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"product-detail__specification-title\">Drying performance</th>\n<td class=\"text-right\">A</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n",
  "description": "<div class=\"media media-feature__description\">\n<div class=\"media-left\"><img class=\"media-object\" src=\"https://whirlpool-cdn.thron.com/delivery/public/thumbnail/whirlpool/lo-33d18fe3-816a-4e38-af8a-73f47d19b644/sckne7/std/500x500/logo.jpg?fill=zoom&amp;fillcolor=rgba:255,255,255&amp;scalemode=product&amp;format=JPEG\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h4 class=\"media-heading\">14 place setting</h4>\n<p><span class=\"product-detail__feature-summary\">Load up to 14 place settings.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media media-feature__description\">\n<div class=\"media-left\"><img class=\"media-object\" src=\"https://whirlpool-cdn.thron.com/delivery/public/thumbnail/whirlpool/lo-906c1372-9e4b-43fe-9f65-5eac15437905/sckne7/std/500x500/logo.jpg?fill=zoom&amp;fillcolor=rgba:255,255,255&amp;scalemode=product&amp;format=JPEG\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h4 class=\"media-heading\">Delay Timer</h4>\n<p><span class=\"product-detail__feature-summary\">The function to delay by up to 24 hours the start of the washing program, allowing you to run the dishwasher at any time of the day, even when youre out.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media media-feature__description\">\n<div class=\"media-left\"><img class=\"media-object\" src=\"https://whirlpool-cdn.thron.com/delivery/public/thumbnail/whirlpool/lo-9a59f567-6fbf-404f-9537-32060ef9401a/sckne7/std/500x500/logo.jpg?fill=zoom&amp;fillcolor=rgba:255,255,255&amp;scalemode=product&amp;format=JPEG\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h4 class=\"media-heading\">Energy class E</h4>\n<p><span class=\"product-detail__feature-summary\">At energy class E this appliance delivers high performance, while always operating in an environmentally-friendly manner.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media media-feature__description\">\n<div class=\"media-left\"><img class=\"media-object\" src=\"https://whirlpool-cdn.thron.com/delivery/public/thumbnail/whirlpool/lo-6df6f6c8-8765-4b04-bd73-e2403e1f0f80/sckne7/std/500x500/logo.jpg?fill=zoom&amp;fillcolor=rgba:255,255,255&amp;scalemode=product&amp;format=JPEG\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h4 class=\"media-heading\">Flexiload</h4>\n<p><span class=\"product-detail__feature-summary\">Flexibility makes space for everything - create additional space in the lower basket by loading pans vertically.</span></div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"media media-feature__description\">\n<div class=\"media-left\"><img class=\"media-object\" src=\"https://whirlpool-cdn.thron.com/delivery/public/thumbnail/whirlpool/lo-21e6efac-f7e5-4dfe-bd65-5314c863277b/sckne7/std/500x500/logo.jpg?fill=zoom&amp;fillcolor=rgba:255,255,255&amp;scalemode=product&amp;format=JPEG\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h4 class=\"media-heading\">Half Load</h4>\n<p><span class=\"product-detail__feature-summary\">The half load option only uses the required amount of energy and water without compromising on performance – designed for when the machine isn't full.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media media-feature__description\">\n<div class=\"media-left\"><img class=\"media-object\" src=\"https://whirlpool-cdn.thron.com/delivery/public/thumbnail/whirlpool/lo-a76a9b79-3425-4008-ae9a-d5716638b30d/sckne7/std/500x500/logo.jpg?fill=zoom&amp;fillcolor=rgba:255,255,255&amp;scalemode=product&amp;format=JPEG\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h4 class=\"media-heading\">Hot water connection</h4>\n<p><span class=\"product-detail__feature-summary\">Possibility to connect water to an hot water pipe (up to 60?). Usage: worldwide buyout for Whirlpool Internet only.</span></div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"media media-feature__description\">\n<div class=\"media-left\"><img class=\"media-object\" src=\"https://whirlpool-cdn.thron.com/delivery/public/thumbnail/whirlpool/lo-54488dcf-aac7-4459-aa2b-6f13692bad64/sckne7/std/500x500/logo.jpg?fill=zoom&amp;fillcolor=rgba:255,255,255&amp;scalemode=product&amp;format=JPEG\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h4 class=\"media-heading\">Inverter Motor</h4>\n<p><span class=\"product-detail__feature-summary\">Thanks to its capacity to vary the spinning speed, the innovative Inverter Motor can properly calibrate water pressure and, therefore, cleaning force, in combination with an optimised electronic control at all times. The magnets allow a precise control of sprayers, directing the water with the right pressure, in the right spot and at the right time.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media media-feature__description\">\n<div class=\"media-left\"><img class=\"media-object\" src=\"https://whirlpool-cdn.thron.com/delivery/public/thumbnail/whirlpool/lo-fb5fe6d2-a048-4670-8ea8-b8e0f566f6e8/sckne7/std/500x500/logo.jpg?fill=zoom&amp;fillcolor=rgba:255,255,255&amp;scalemode=product&amp;format=JPEG\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h4 class=\"media-heading\">Intensive</h4>\n<p><span class=\"product-detail__feature-summary\">A dedicated program for heavily soiled crockery, with burnt food residuals, especially suitable for pans and saucepans.</span></div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"media media-feature__description\">\n<div class=\"media-left\"><img class=\"media-object\" src=\"https://whirlpool-cdn.thron.com/delivery/public/thumbnail/whirlpool/lo-dd316cb6-b635-45e2-9f07-8abe785291af/sckne7/std/500x500/logo.jpg?fill=zoom&amp;fillcolor=rgba:255,255,255&amp;scalemode=product&amp;format=JPEG\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h4 class=\"media-heading\">Overflow</h4>\n<p><span class=\"product-detail__feature-summary\">Passive water protection system which detects leakages in the tub and prevents flooding in the house. In case of rupture of the tub, the water leaks into the lower compartment of the machine where the floating device triggers the fault alarm. Drain pump is activated and the tub is emptied.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media media-feature__description\">\n<div class=\"media-left\"><img class=\"media-object\" src=\"https://whirlpool-cdn.thron.com/delivery/public/thumbnail/whirlpool/lo-96b9021d-ab9f-4919-a508-5abe72ab12d1/sckne7/std/500x500/logo.jpg?fill=zoom&amp;fillcolor=rgba:255,255,255&amp;scalemode=product&amp;format=JPEG\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h4 class=\"media-heading\">Rack lift up</h4>\n<p><span class=\"product-detail__feature-summary\">The adjustable 2nd rack can be moved up or down to create additional space to fit taller or bulky items.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media media-feature__description\">\n<div class=\"media-left\"><img class=\"media-object\" src=\"https://whirlpool-cdn.thron.com/delivery/public/thumbnail/whirlpool/lo-b323a62e-f3a0-4ee9-8231-d25d949e0005/sckne7/std/500x500/logo.jpg?fill=zoom&amp;fillcolor=rgba:255,255,255&amp;scalemode=product&amp;format=JPEG\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h4 class=\"media-heading\">Stainless Steel interior</h4>\n<p><span class=\"product-detail__feature-summary\">A long lasting stainless steel tough interior that protects and cleans.</span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media media-feature__description\">\n<div class=\"media-left\"><img class=\"media-object\" src=\"https://whirlpool-cdn.thron.com/delivery/public/thumbnail/whirlpool/lo-8d47179d-6438-45ba-b098-6f620b1cedbe/sckne7/std/500x500/logo.jpg?fill=zoom&amp;fillcolor=rgba:255,255,255&amp;scalemode=product&amp;format=JPEG\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"media-body\">\n<h4 class=\"media-heading\">Tablet</h4>\n<p><span class=\"product-detail__feature-summary\">It maximizes the efficiency of the detergent multi-use tabs.</span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n",
